|8 |  │         ├─HASH JOIN        |                      |13      |1028        |
|9 |  │         │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|household_demographics|1       |15          |
|10|  │         │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN|store_sales           |5000    |594         |
|11|  │         └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |date_dim              |162     |55          |
|12|  └─TABLE GET                  |customer              |1       |16          |
=================================================================================
